subject: Re: Nissan the movie.
author: Tim
full_text:
Frank,

Very interesting.  It's been a while since I've listenend to your files.  The fm on this tuner sounds really active; the Others are definitely chatty on this band. 

This is what I hear (in studio grade headphones):

Your AM file @ 03 secs: "Here  Prin  Cess" (male + two escalating                   tones)
             @ 11 secs: "Be sure (static) good news" (male)

Your FM file @ 01 secs: "Trying to get through" (in female tones)
             @ 03 secs: "It don't ?boost? right" (male then two tones)
             @ 05 secs: "Closer to cooperating?" (male, first vowel sound is hard and second vowel sound in this word is a soft 'a' or 'o' so it cannot be calamity)
             @ 06 secs: "Till we're done" (female, fast)
             @ 08 secs: "Frank" (male)
             @ 09 secs: "Hi" (female singing, drawn out)       
             @ 11 secs: "How you doing" (male)
             @ 14 secs: "Hi" (female or child)

Tim W.
